{"tid":2458231,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人小學玩話劇試過做性別反串角色","createTime":"2021-03-23T09:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T12:21:44.000Z","uid":4618,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fb02f9012513182c5eebe7a759a816bd5b515840","tid":2458231,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:14:40.000Z","msg":"記得係有一年中文堂搞咩班際話劇比賽，我明明係女仔被人叫咗去做王子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過最慘都唔係我，有個男同學被我地半強逼咁逼咗去做公主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n登台嗰日成班女同學都好認真，帶晒化妝品返學校，打粉底眼影睫毛紅唇搞晒成套，當然要著埋公主裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後當然不出意係我地嗰班全場最爆，我同佢雙雙拎最佳男女主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後佢就多咗個花名叫「校草」，經過走廊有啲高年級姐姐都會咁叫佢，個情景就好似火盃的考驗，啲女學生見到哈利都會「你好波特」咁叫，次次都笑死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知經過咁多年佢仲會唔會有童年陰影，我小學其他嘢都唔太記得，最深印象就係條友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2a82c7679e97e65df0e1aef86f3c371cdef542","tid":2458231,"uid":276382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"少女漫畫必有劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c012b9540c84ee577c0c0153e3904242b2536ef","tid":2458231,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c2a82c7679e97e65df0e1aef86f3c371cdef542","tid":2458231,"uid":276382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"少女漫畫必有劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:18:26.000Z","msg":"嗰時唔會咁諗，依家睇返又真係幾少女漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee6c3ad3acf7f1f9f3fa4123d46d94f2d126be2","tid":2458231,"uid":223082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:21:45.000Z","msg":"差唔多次次話劇都要搵啲麻甩佬扮女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係唔核突唔扮"},{"pid":"9c9b9354ae50c05e24d75370b7b1f32935e8e5bb","tid":2458231,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ee6c3ad3acf7f1f9f3fa4123d46d94f2d126be2","tid":2458231,"uid":223082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:21:45.000Z","msg":"差唔多次次話劇都要搵啲麻甩佬扮女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係唔核突唔扮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:23:32.000Z","msg":"好仆街，呢啲真係扮一次記成世<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0309f8237d4cd28df8e1f7e355b4eb8972f0dc1","tid":2458231,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5803511d7e7dcaccc920f464a852d783d37ca2","tid":2458231,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:33:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32c6789ed06a00220f2dff906f60196b141c063","tid":2458231,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec6e9be01a132a47c0a3447b6fc000c26b454c0","tid":2458231,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b803fe695fde6b49f945e072718af7ac93c080","tid":2458231,"uid":59799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:55:54.000Z","msg":"小櫻小狼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b429083ffb4426ccc7c4430f26a66baa2957e4","tid":2458231,"uid":223299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"試過聖誕節話劇做女性山羊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed20d914b1ffac2f54d8d5f53b261855e9b9c0c4","tid"